source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_SEQ_00<tab>Fibubb Gah seeks your aid in preserving the Amalj'aa holy land.

TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_SEQ_01<tab>You have accepted the duty of removing a dire threat to the sacred lands of Zanr'ak. Slaughter bronze tortoises until Lacovie appears, then slay the ever-spawning matriarch herself.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_SEQ_01<tab>Fibubb Gah vous a chargé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> d'éliminer trois des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209CF0302 /var> res<var 16 /var>pon<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>bles de nuisances dans les environs, mais surtout d'abattre <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F209380202 /var>, chef de la troupe.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_SEQ_02<tab>You have defeated the ground-shaking Lacovie. Return to the Ring of Ash and report to Fibubb Gah.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez vaincu plusieurs <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209CF0302 /var> et leur chef <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F209380202 /var>. Il est temps d'aller faire votre rapport à Fibubb Gah.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_SEQ_03<tab>You have delivered news of your success to Fibubb Gah. Though pleased with your deeds, the Brotherhood soldier warns that the emergence of a new matriarch is only a matter of time.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_SEQ_03<tab>Fibubb Gah s'est montré satisfait de vos résultats. Il espère que les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209CF0302 /var> ne provoqueront plus de dégâts pendant quelque temps.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_TODO_00<tab>Slay three bronze tortoises, then defeat Lacovie when she appears.

target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_TODO_01<tab>Faire un rapport à Fibubb Gah

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_001<tab>For we Amalj'aa, Zanr'ak is more than merely dust and rock─it is sacred ground. The preservation of this holy land is our duty and our privilege.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_001<tab>Une terre sacrée, Zanr'ak est pour nous Amalj'aa. La protéger, notre devoir est. Des dégâts, les êtres doués de la parole provoquent. Mais l'endommager, la faune peut aussi.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_002<tab>One of the greatest threats to its delicate balance are the voracious bronze tortoises. These insatiable creatures wander as their appetite leads them, feeding without surcease. Slaughtering them brings little respite, for they multiply at a seemingly unnatural pace.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_002<tab>Un problème, les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209CF0302 /var> posent aujourd'hui. La végétation, elles saccagent par gloutonnerie. Sans fin, elles se multiplient. Une tragédie pour l'équilibre local, leur prolifération est.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_003<tab>No, honored ally, I would have you dispatch their matriarch─the mighty Lacovie. It is she that spawns her shell-backed children in such uncontrollable numbers.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_003<tab>D'intervenir, il est temps. La meneuse du groupe, <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F209380202 /var>, tu vas devoir éliminer. Pulluler, elles ne pourront plus sans elle.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_004<tab>To draw out the mother, however, you must first endanger her offspring. Slay the lesser tortoises, and the matriarch will soon appear. With her crushing weight and snapping jaws, you will find Lacovie a worthy adversary.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_004<tab>Difficile, trouver <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F209380202 /var> pourrait se révéler. Vaincre des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209CF0302 /var>, il faudrait alors pour l'attirer. Puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> guerri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>, cette mission je te confie.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_011<tab>Slay the bronze tortoises that ravage Zanr'ak, and Lacovie will come seeking vengeance. May glory and honor guide your arm.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_011<tab>D'attirer <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F209380202 /var>, vaincre des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209CF0302 /var> te permettra. Puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> guerri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>, cette mission je te confie.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_021<tab>With the death of Lacovie, you have slain a great threat to our holy land. It should be many years before another tortoise attains her size and claims the matriarch's name.
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_021<tab><var 2B ((<var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F209380202 /var>)) /var>, tu as vaincu<var 1D /var>! Du beau travail, éliminer leur chef était. Sans elle, infester nos terres les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209CF0302 /var> ne devraient plus.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_022<tab>But we must not grow complacent. The sky-fires that seared the realm have shaken the foundations of all that we knew to be true...
target: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_FIBUBBGAH_000_022<tab>Sévir de nouveau, ces maudites carapaces pourraient. Appel à toi je ferai alors.

source: TEXT_BANAMA104_01225_TORTOISE_BALLOON_001<tab>Lacovie has come to avenge her offspring!
